Package model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder

The collection of path finding algorithms.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStarNode
    An A* node is a node used in the AStarPathFinder.
    AStarPathFinder
    The A* Path Finder uses the A* algorithm to find a path from a start Position to a goal Position.
    DijkstraNode
    The Dijkstra Node class represents a specific node in the Dijkstra graph, used in the DijkstraPathFinder.
    DijkstraPathFinder
    The Dijkstra Path Finder uses the Dijkstra algorithm to find a path from a start Position to a goal Position.
    JumpPointNode
    A jump point search node.
    JumpPointSearchPathFinder
    The jump point search path finder uses jump point search to determine paths.
    PathFinder
    A path finder finds a feasible path between a specified starting Position and goal Position on a specified Map.
